sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant UI as Button (ProtectedAction)
    participant Local as LocalStorage
    participant Router as NextRouter
    participant Handler as ParentComponent (OnAction)

    User->>UI: 버튼 클릭 (예: 좋아요, 글쓰기 등)
    
    UI->>Local: getItem("accessToken")
    activate UI
    
    alt 토큰 없음 (비로그인)
        UI->>Router: push("/login")
        Router-->>User: 로그인 페이지 이동
    else 토큰 있음 (로그인)
        UI->>Handler: onAction() 콜백 실행
        activate Handler
        Handler->>Handler: 실제 기능 수행 (API 호출 등)
        deactivate Handler
    end
    deactivate UI